text: Sevdalina Teokharova (; born 24 July 1974) is a Bulgarian rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
